<br>
Creapiing slowly came to an awareness. She felt the hard stone beneath her body and opened her eyes to see the Thresher of the Harvest by her side. Khasiraths body had an unnatural ashen hue. Too weak to even raise her hand, she said in a barely audible whisper ~you smell like fish~ before laying back and closing her eyes again<br>
